<div class="row" id="§deepscan">
    <div class="col-lg-8  col-lg-offset-2">
        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h1 class="panel-title">Primer design for semi-random mutagenesis</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-body">
                <h2>Mutantprimers</h2>
                <h3>Description</h3>
                <p>This tool designs QuickChange primers in bulk, either traditional or staggered, like the Deepscan tool, except that the amino acid mutations required are specified.
                    This includes options for degerate codons (see <a href="#codon_scheme_descriptor">below</a>).</p>
                <h3>Input</h3>
                    <div class="col-lg-12"><p>To make primers at the ends of the coding sequence, the neighbouring
                        noncoding sequence are required.
                        Two options are available:</p>
                        <input type="radio" name="MP_opt" value="split" checked> To give the upstream and downstream sequence
                        separately.<br/>
                        <input type="radio" name="MP_opt" value="pos"> To give a sequence with a start and end position. A variant
                        of this is to give the
                        starting/end position as a short sequence to match as opposed to a number.<br/>
                        <br/></div>
                    <!--
                    <div class="col-lg-5">
                        <div class="input-group">
                    <span class="input-group-addon" data-toggle="tooltip"
                          title="Choose input method."
                          data-placement="top">Choose given:</span>
                            <input type="checkbox" class="switch" id="MP_choose" checked data-off-text="2"
                                   data-on-text="1" data-off-color="warning" data-size="large" checked>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    -->
                <!--</div>-->
                <div class="form-group">

                    <div id="MP_upSequence_group">
                        <div class="input-group">
                        <span class="input-group-addon" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top"
                              title="Sequence of the upstream region to prime off.">Upstream<br/>Sequence
                        </span>
                            <textarea class="form-control custom-control" rows="5" style="resize:none"
                                      id="MP_upSequence"
                                      name="upsequence"></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <br/>
                    </div>
                    <div id="MP_sequence_group">
                        <div class="input-group">
                        <span class="input-group-addon" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top"
                              title="Sequence with some of the upstream and downstream region to prime off if position mode active, else just the coding sequence.">Sequence
                        </span>
                            <textarea class="form-control custom-control" rows="5" style="resize:none" id="MP_sequence"
                                      name="sequence"></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <br/></div>
                    <div id="MP_downSequence_group">
                        <div class="input-group">
                        <span class="input-group-addon" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top"
                              title="Sequence with downstream region to prime off.">Downstream<br/>Sequence
                        </span>
                            <textarea class="form-control custom-control" rows="5" style="resize:none"
                                      id="MP_downSequence"
                                      name="downsequence"></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <br/>
                    </div>
                    &nbsp;
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-4" id="MP_startBase_group">
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <span class="input-group-addon" data-toggle="tooltip"
                                      title="The value can be a number —the first base of the given sequence will be 1— or a short sequence starting with the first base of the target"
                                      data-placement="top">First base</span>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="MP_startBase"
                                       placeholder="number or string">
                            </div>
                            <br/>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-4" id="MP_stopBase_group">
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <span class="input-group-addon" data-toggle="tooltip"
                                      title="The value can be a number —the first base of the given sequence will be 1— or a short sequence ending with the last base of the target"
                                      data-placement="top"> Last base</span>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="MP_stopBase" placeholder="number or string">
                            </div>
                            <br/>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-9" id="codon_scheme_descriptor">
                            <p>Add to the following textarea the list of mutations desired, such as A13P. If more complex mutations, such as degenerate codons are to be use mark the destination codon in square brakets after the AA residue and its number, <i>e.g.</i> A13[NNK]. For mutations to multiple amino acids (<i>e.g.</i> A13GP) please specify the required codon for now. If considering degenerate codons and are not sure which to pick, try using the helper tool.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-3"><button class="btn btn-info" type="button" data-toggle="modal"
                                        data-target="#scheme_modal"><i
                                        class="fa fa-flask" aria-hidden="true"></i> helper tool</button><br/><br/></div>
                        </div><div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-12">
                            <div id="MP_mutationList_group">
                        <div class="input-group">
                        <span class="input-group-addon" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top"
                              title="Sequence with downstream region to prime off.">Mutation<br/>List
                        </span>
                            <textarea class="form-control custom-control" rows="5" style="resize:none"
                                      id="MP_mutationList"
                                      name="mutationList"></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <br/>
                    </div>
                            <br/>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-4">
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <span class="input-group-addon warning" data-toggle="tooltip"
                                      title="Enzyme system used, which affects the Tm"
                                      data-placement="top">Enzyme</span>
                                <select class="form-control" id="MP_enzyme">
                                    <option value="1">no salts (+0&deg;C)</option>
                                    <option value="2">50 mM Na (+2.8&deg;C)</option>
                                    <option value="3">Taq buffer (+4.9&deg;C)</option>
                                    <option value="4" selected="selected">Phusion buffer (+11.6&deg;C)</option>
                                    <option value="5">Q5 buffer (+13.3&deg;C)</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                            <br/>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-4">
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <span class="input-group-addon" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Target melting temperature"
                                      data-placement="top">Target T<sub>m</sub></span>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="55" id="MP_targetTemp">
                            </div>
                            <br/>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-4">
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <span class="input-group-addon" data-toggle="tooltip"
                                      title="&deg;C tollerance for GC clamp" data-placement="top">GC clamp bonus</span>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="1" id="MP_GCclamp">
                            </div>
                            <br/>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-4">
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <span class="input-group-addon" data-toggle="tooltip"
                                      title="Method used: full overlap (traditional) of primers or staggered overlap"
                                      data-placement="top">Method</span>
                                <input type="checkbox" class="switch" id="MP_method" checked data-off-text="Full"
                                       data-on-text="Stagger" data-switch-value="large" data-off-color="warning"
                                       checked>
                            </div>
                            <br/>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-4">
                            <div class="input-group" id="MP_overlap_group">
                                <span class="input-group-addon" data-toggle="tooltip" title="The length of the overlap"
                                      data-placement="top">Overlap</span>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="22" id="MP_overlap">
                            </div>
                            <br/>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-4">
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <span class="input-group-addon" data-toggle="tooltip"
                                      title="Total length range of the primers" data-placement="top">Length</span>
                                <input id="MP_primerRange" type="text" class="form-control span2 slider" value=""
                                       data-slider-min="18" data-slider-max="60" data-slider-step="1"
                                       data-slider-value="[22,40]"/>
                            </div>
                            <br/>
                        </div>


                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3">
                            <div class="btn-group" role="group" aria-label="...">
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-warning" id="MP_clear"><i class="fa fa-eraser"
                                                                                               aria-hidden="true"></i>
                                    Clear
                                </button>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-info" id="MP_demo"><i class="fa fa-files-o"
                                                                                           aria-hidden="true"></i> Demo
                                </button>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-success" id="MP_calculate"><i
                                        class="fa fa-exchange" aria-hidden="true"></i> Calculate
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <br/>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row hidden" id="MP_download">
                        <h3>Downloads</h3>
                        <br/>
                        <div class="col-lg-3">Dowload results as:</div>

                        <div class="col-lg-9">
                            <div class="btn-group" role="group" aria-label="...">
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-success" id="MP_table"><i class="fa fa-bars"
                                                                                               aria-hidden="true"></i>
                                    CSV
                                </button>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-warning" id="MP_json"><i class="fa fa-cog"
                                                                                              aria-hidden="true"></i>
                                    JSON
                                </button>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-info" id="MP_IDT_bulk"><i
                                        class="fa fa-shopping-basket" aria-hidden="true"></i> IDT bulk
                                </button>
                                <a class="btn btn-info" id="MP_IDT_plate96" href='/deepscan_IDT96'
                                   download="deepscan_primers_IDT96.xlsx"><i class="fa fa-shopping-cart"
                                                                             aria-hidden="true"></i> IDT 96-plate
                                </a>
                                <a class="btn btn-info" id="MP_IDT_plate384" href='/deepscan_IDT384'
                                   download="deepscan_primers_IDT384.xlsx"><i class="fa fa-shopping-cart"
                                                                              aria-hidden="true"></i> IDT 384-plate
                                </a>

                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <br/>


                    </div>
                    <div class="row hidden" id="MP_result">
                        <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert"><span class="pycorpse"></span> Oh Snap. Something
                            went wrong
                        </div>
                        <br/>
                    </div>

                    <br/>
